                    <desc type="CalendaricNote">
                    Calendar of the Weevily and Unweevely Months, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐሳበ፡ ዕፀዋት፡ ጽንዕት፡ ወጽንጽንት፡</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a5">
                    <locus target="#iiiv(erso)" facs="004">Fol. iiiv(erso)</locus>
